Rosanne Hull-Brown https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosanne_Hull-Brown 0 Rosanne Hull-Brown is an Australian actress, who remains best known for her performance as Merle Jones during the final year (1986) of the television drama series Prisoner. She subsequently left acting and became a music teacher.
